data.description: Beautiful Well Kept 4 Bed 2 Bath Home On 1.5 Acres Located In the Desirable Savannah Heights Neighborhood. This Home Boasts Wood Pattern Laminate Flooring Throughout, Bonus Wrap Around Kitchen Cabinets, Huge Master Bath And Closet. This Manicured Oak Studded Property Is Perfect For Relaxing And Getting Away From It All While Being Ever So Close To Major City/Towns. Not To Mention Being Able To Unwind In The Recently Installed Jacuzzi That Is Conveying With The Sale Of The Home. All Appliances Along With Riding Mower In Backyard Will Also Convey With Sale Of The Home. The Neighborhood Has Their Own Private Pond And Playground Ideal For Picnics Or Leisure Days. Not To Mention The Sense Of Community It Gives With The Numerous Events And Activities Bringing Out A Truly Unique Living Experience. Come See How This House Can Become Your Home.
